{
  "stem": "12029.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came-- I don't know how he knew, he came to that woman, and he said that my father is alive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That Pole, what he was a friend of my father, he had  a friend, an SS man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this SS man was a rather nice man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For money, he would do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said he would go to the ghetto to bring my father, but he can't go at night because the Jews are shooting at night.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it start, the uprising in the ghetto, it started before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was standing behind the curtain watching, burning the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you imagine our hearts when we were there, and we saw the ghetto is burning, and we couldn't do nothing to help?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I forgot to tell you that when we were-- before the ghetto start burning, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] my father used to collect money in the ghetto, send out, and they used to send guns and ammunition into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the-- you know, those-- those fellows which collected the-- the German uniforms, they came with a cart with horses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the cart, they put it in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they bought pumps and all different-- that people should hide in the ghetto, you know, underneath, and my husband used to organize it all.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wasn't my husband then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was my uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then when the ghetto start burning, they were shooting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my friend then came out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [LAUGHS] The German said that he will go, if that young man would stay there overnight, and collect my father.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
